abstract.text: Catalog SHPE events, track attendance, and stay updated with the latest activities at the University of Florida.

inlineContent.text: SHPE UF Mobile App provides students with a way to explore and track SHPE events on campus. You can view event details, check event maps, and receive real-time notifications.
The app is designed to help users:
View detailed event locations with MapsView
Track personal event attendance through PointsView
